snippet.title: Evercade - Arcade Cartridges Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
ARCADE IS HERE!

Four great collections of classic arcade titles and hidden gems are coming to Evercade. Playable on Handheld and Evercade VS!

Coming November 2021! Find out more below:
Technos Arcade 1: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/technos-arcade-1/
Data East Arcade 1: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/data-east-arcade-1/
Gaelco Aracde 1: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/gaelco-arcade-1/
Atari Aracde 1: https://evercade.co.uk/cartridges/atari-arcade-1
